/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/gooddollar_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/round_summary_stderr.log:62:    "impact": "A stale governance key can continue minting G$ through `mintRewardFromRR` and can still reconfigure distribution recipients. Rotating governance therefore does not actually remove protocol control from the old avatar, enabling unauthorized inflation, value extraction, and long-lived control over where future distributions are sent.",
