/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/gooddollar_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Governance_rotation_leaves_former_avatar/poc_prompt_repair_5.md:24:- title: Governance rotation leaves former avatar with permanent reserve minting and helper admin powers
