/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/gooddollar_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Governance_rotation_leaves_former_avatar/poc_prompt_repair_2.md:24:- title: Governance rotation leaves former avatar with permanent reserve minting and helper admin powers
/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/gooddollar_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_Governance_rotation_leaves_former_avatar/poc_prompt_repair_2.md:25:- claim: `GoodReserveCDai` and `DistributionHelper` snapshot the current `avatar` into `AccessControl` roles during initialization, but those roles are never revoked or automatically reassigned when `Controller.avatar()` changes. After governance rotation, the former avatar still keeps `RESERVE_MINTER_ROLE` on the reserve and `DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE` on the helper.
